PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of MELVIN WOODWARD, of Goose Bay, Newfoundland, as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending April 30, 1999, in the place of Mervyn C. Russell.
